General.Name: Alzinova AB
General.Description: Alzinova AB (publ), a biopharma company, engages in the development of an active immunotherapy for the treatment of Alzheimer's disease in Sweden. Its lead candidate is ALZ-101, an oligomer-specific vaccine for the treatment of Alzheimer's disease; and ALZ-201, a monoclonal antibody that neutralizes the toxic oligomers. The company was founded in 2011 and is based in Mölndal, Sweden.
